OL,3,CChairman of West Midlands Police
OL,4,CFederation suspended
OL,6,FThe chairman of the West Midlands
OL,7,FPolice Federation has been suspended
OL,8,Fafter he branded racism allegations as
OL,9,F"nonsense".
OL,11,FRichard Cooke made the comment on
OL,12,Fsocial media after a former chief
OL,13,Finspector alleged racism and
OL,14,Fhomophobia were rife within the force.
OL,16,FThe Police Federation of England and
OL,17,FWales (PFEW) said it received multiple
OL,18,Fcomplaints about Mr Cooke's post.
OL,20,FMr Cooke has told ITV News Central he
OL,21,Fhas done "nothing wrong".
