OL,6,FThe PFEW has released a statement. A
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We can confirm
OL,8,Fthat the Chair of the West Midlands
OL,9,FFederation Branch, Richard Cooke, has
OL,10,Fbeen suspended from his duties as
OL,11,FChair pending an investigation under
OL,12,Fthe Police Federation's rules which
OL,13,Fstipulate expected standards from a
OL,14,FFed representative.
OL,16,F"An independent investigating officer
OL,17,Fhas been appointed, and we hope that
OL,18,Fthe matter can be brought to a timely
OL,19,Fconclusion."
