OL,6,FIn response, Mr Cooke said he is
OL,7,F"seeking legal advice and will
OL,8,Fstaunchly defend myself".
OL,10,FIn a statement sent to ITV News
OL,11,FCentral, he wrote: "All I have done is
OL,12,Fdefend our members from
OL,13,Fsensationalised headlines alleging
OL,14,F"widespread racism" & a "gang culture".
OL,16,FHe added: "These are wrong and
OL,17,Fmisleading. This is the view of our
OL,18,Fbranch board and I stand by everything
OL,19,FI have said on their behalf.
